WEBVTT


00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:02.900
Recent update to health and care visa

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:09.600
care workers

00:00:09.600 --> 00:00:12.680
and senior care worker will no longer be able to bring

00:00:12.680 --> 00:00:14.720
dependents to UK from overseas.

00:00:14.720 --> 00:00:17.180
Starting from spring 2024,

00:00:25.360 --> 00:00:27.920
students switching into care within UK

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:29.440
will not be allowed to switch

00:00:29.440 --> 00:00:30.640
along with their dependent.

00:00:30.640 --> 00:00:32.900
Starting April 2024.

00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:42.920
Students dependents switching

00:00:42.920 --> 00:00:45.960
into care will not be allowed to switch their spouses

00:00:45.960 --> 00:00:48.320
into care visa to become their dependent

00:00:48.320 --> 00:00:50.580
starting April 2024.

00:00:57.280 --> 00:01:01.220
Follow for latest updates. 24 7 share repost.
